==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: -ferous
<hw>-fer*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>-fer</ets>. fr. ferre to
bear. See <er>Bear</er> to support.]</ety> <def>A suffix signifying
<sig>bearing</sig>, <sig>producing</sig>, <sig>yielding</sig>; <as>as,
